two types of controllers

Simple Controller

php artisan make:controller TestController 


Resource Controller

php artisan make:controller TestController --resource



4 types of Route(Must connect controller)

Api   ->   

channels -> trigger events

 
console ->

web -> front-end 

route/web.php

Route::get("hello", 'TestController@index'); connect simple controller

Route::resource("another", 'AnotherController'); connect resource controller


php artisan make:model Blog
